These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, italian, japanese, thai, turkish
7 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, go, domino, monopoly, bridge, whist
 1. the australian is between the italian and the turkish##2
 2. the french is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 4. the japanese is between the person playing go and the person playing monopoly##2
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the person playing billiard is between the person playing domino and the person playing go##2
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the thai##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | italian | australian | turkish | french    | indonesian | japanese   | thai    |
| Game         | bridge  | mah-jongg   | domino | billiard | go   | whist | monopoly |

