.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, alhambra, pall-mall, tiparillo, fonseca, blend, bolivar
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the italian##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Cigar          | fonseca | pall-mall | blend | alhambra | bolivar | davidoff      | tiparillo  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

