.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, skateboarding, sailing, baseball, parkour, cricket
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Sport   | cricket | baseball | water-polo | basketball   | sailing | skateboarding | parkour |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

