.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, balloon-flower, orchid, iris, zinnia, aconite
1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsiris is the fan of disco##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person who growstulip is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Flower     | tulip | zinnia | aconite       | rose | balloon-flower | iris | orchid |

