 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person playing bridge##2
